dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n打咁撚大篇嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T07:54:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T07:54:43.000Z","msg":"蓋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T11:27:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19a56f2cdce69f0476d8f4dbbc335304f6f68493","tid":1174184,"uid":19527,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T11:29:45.000Z","msg":"利靠黑哨"},{"pid":"faeae9bd6ebe14b18c8764bf70290213d340b966","tid":1174184,"uid":224771,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T11:33:02.000Z","msg":"真心有啲羨慕<br />\n哩兩隊都唔似曼咁多勝利球迷<br />\n雖然而家猁都唔少<br />\n班人一輸波就要搵人屌 又永遠要用費格遜時期黎比<br />\n唔知以為呢隊波係費格遜聯隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n要有即時成績 又要屌買人貴<br />\n要班年輕球員即刻打出球星級表現 又唔會容許佢哋犯錯<br />\n睇Lindelof 摩佬走前死用佢 就算佢係咁派膠都用 半季就變左全隊最勁嗰個中堅<br />\nRashford Martial Lingard Pogba Lkk 又永遠用C朗黎比 明明本身C朗都係萬中無一<br />\n反而利 熱 啲球迷唔會有過高期望（起碼喺公海見到係）<br />\n唔好同我講話球迷意見唔會影響球員球會<br />\n啲投票佢地一定見到 佢哋上社交網站既時候一定會見到啲人點屌佢地"}]}